sequenceDiagram
    participant User as External User
    participant GW as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Auth as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Notebook as Notebook Pod<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant KServe as KServe Controller
    participant vLLM as vLLM Runtime<br/>8000/HTTP, 8033/gRPC
    participant GuardGW as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/HTTP
    participant GuardOrch as fms-guardrails-orchestrator<br/>8034/HTTP
    participant Detectors as guardrails-detectors<br/>8080/HTTP
    participant DSPAPI as DSP API Server<br/>8888/HTTP
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows<br/>2746/HTTPS
    participant MLMD as ml-metadata<br/>8080/gRPC
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as model-registry<br/>8080/HTTP
    participant MLflow as MLflow<br/>5000/HTTP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh<br/>8033/gRPC
    participant RestProxy as rest-proxy<br/>8008/HTTP

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Model Serving (KServe RawDeployment)
    User->>GW: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    GW->>Auth: ext_authz check<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS (service-ca)
    Auth-->>GW: Auth OK (Bearer token)
    GW->>vLLM: HTTPRoute forward<br/>HTTP/8000
    vLLM-->>GW: Prediction Response
    GW-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Model Serving (ModelMesh)
    User->>ModelMesh: HTTPS/8443 via oauth-proxy
    ModelMesh->>RestProxy: gRPC/8033
    RestProxy->>ModelMesh: REST 8008 to gRPC 8033
    ModelMesh->>S3: Cache miss - load model<br/>HTTPS/443, Access Key
    S3-->>ModelMesh: Model artifacts
    ModelMesh-->>User: Inference response

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: LLM Serving with Guardrails
    User->>GuardGW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/8090
    GuardGW->>GuardOrch: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8034
    GuardOrch->>Detectors: Input detection<br/>HTTP/8080
    Detectors-->>GuardOrch: Detection results
    GuardOrch->>vLLM: LLM inference<br/>HTTP/8000
    vLLM-->>GuardOrch: Generated text
    GuardOrch->>Detectors: Output detection<br/>HTTP/8080
    Detectors-->>GuardOrch: Detection results
    GuardOrch-->>GuardGW: Guardrailed response
    GuardGW-->>User: Safe response

    Note over User,S3: Flow 4: Pipeline Execution (KFP v2)
    User->>GW: Create Pipeline Run<br/>HTTPS/443
    GW->>Auth: ext_authz check
    Auth-->>GW: Auth OK
    GW->>DSPAPI: HTTPRoute forward<br/>HTTP/8888
    DSPAPI->>Argo: Create Workflow<br/>HTTPS/2746
    Argo->>Argo: Spawn workflow pods
    Argo->>MLMD: Log artifacts/executions<br/>gRPC/8080
    Argo->>S3: Store artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over User,S3: Flow 5: Notebook Workbench
    User->>GW: Access notebook<br/>HTTPS/443
    GW->>Auth: OAuth2/OIDC auth<br/>HTTPS/8443
    Auth-->>GW: Auth OK + Bearer token
    GW->>Notebook: HTTPRoute forward<br/>HTTP/8888

    Note over User,S3: Flow 6: Model Registry Integration
    KServe->>ModelReg: Sync InferenceService state<br/>HTTP/8080
    vLLM->>ModelReg: CSI storage initializer<br/>model-registry:// URI
    ModelReg-->>vLLM: Model artifacts location
